narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Recommend it for anyone who is interested in how archaeology is done in the field. Also recommend it for a good Social credit if you can make the weekend trips -FUN!!! (my semester it was the Saturdays in October). The class is about Grad students so it also allows you to meet some people besides undergrads.
See reviews for ARCH 277 (the other half of this class).
I would recommend this class, as it and its partner is a great introduction to field work and excavations.
